      <hr>
      <h3>INPUT CONVENTIONS</h3>
      <div class="description2"><strong>Punctuation and Spacing</strong> - Punctuation and spacing conventions described in the name heading <em>General
                           Information</em> sections are also applicable to the Heading ($b) and
                     Title ($t) subfields in field 663. Field 663 does not end with a mark of
                     punctuation unless the data ends with an abbreviation, an initial/ letter, or data that
                     ends with a mark of punctuation.
      </div>
